Package: core-linux
Architecture: any
Depends: bash (>= 5.0), curl, git, jq, fzf, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Modular Development Environment for Linux terminals
 core-linux provides a unified CLI and TUI for managing development
 tools, languages, databases, AI assistants, and more.
 It features a modular architecture with 8+ modules, each containing
 multiple tools that can be installed individually via flags.
